### INSTRUCTIONS ###

# 1. {COPY} the required domain(s) script from the "./domain-list" folder to the "./domains" folder.

# 2. Modify the copied scripts as necessary to fit your $SERVERS & $DOMAIN conditions.

# 3. Make sure there is a "deploy.sh" and a "dnsimple.ini" files in the "./domains" folder. There is a backup in ./domains-list

# 4. Run the "master.sh" script as a SUDOER USER. NO SUDO in the command itself. Check Console Output for any critical errors! Some errors pertaining to "shred" are ok. Double check!!

# 5. Run the "cleanup.sh" script


